data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! All offers will be considered. Custom farmhouse nestled on approximately 4.97 acres, accompanied by a charming 400 sq ft detached guest house. Thoughtfully renovated within the last two years, this residence boasts a plethora of enhancements, including a fully remodeled and redesigned kitchen with top-tier appliances, an upgraded primary bathroom, and a reconfigured floor plan incorporating a third full bathroom. Revel in the new laundry room, a walk-in butler's pantry with a sink, and a stylish beverage bar. The house welcomes you with an iron double swing entry door, vaulted ceilings, beautiful wood laminate floors, and farmhouse character with shiplap walls and crown molding accents. Great floor plan featuring a private primary bedroom, a separate bedroom with an en-suite, a third bedroom with double closets, and a third full bathroom available for guests. The guest house underwent its own transformation, featuring all new windows, all new flooring, full-size washer/dryer connections, a convenient kitchenette, and a full bathroom. Both the main house and the guest retreat received new metal roofs in 2021. The backyard is complete with a new two-stall run-in barn with a tack room and a new chicken coop. Noteworthy is the potential to assume a 2.5% VA loan, providing a valuable financing option. This property is currently ag exempt. Contact me for additional information.
